<HEADLINE>
<P>
CHINA PUTS 9 TO DEATH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
BEIJING 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Nine Chinese in the southern city of Canton were executed for gun-running, 
robbery and murder and four men in Shanghai were sentenced to death for 
corruption, according to official reports reaching Beijing Friday. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
