MID VALLEY ARC WINS 3 TITLES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Mid Valley American Roundball Corp. won three age-group team championships in 
the Las Vegas Easter Classic on Saturday. 
</P>
<P>
Crenshaw High's Kevin Ollie, the tournament's most valuable player, hit a bank 
shot with three seconds remaining to give Mid Valley a 69-68 win over Orange 
County's Orange Express in the 17-and-under championship game. David Harbour of 
Camarillo scored nine points. 
</P>
