we have the same goals in mind.' -- Raul Perez, Huntington Park city councilman 
; Photo, 'I'm going to talk to each and every councilman and try to bury the 
hatchet so we can move forward.'Luis Hernandez, Huntington Park city councilman 
AXEL KOESTER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
