Minnesota's Gary Gaetti, who was out at the plate in the fourth. ; Photo, 
COLOR, Lance Parrish, left, receives congratulations from Angel teammate 
Claudell Washington after hitting a two-run home run during the fourth inning. 
CHARISTINE WALTER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
