<HEADLINE>
<P>
BETTING WITH BOB 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Times handicapper Bob Mieszerski lost $18 Saturday when Dearly Loved finished 
third in the eighth race to ruin his $9 triple bet after Fashionable Flair and 
Big Bass won the sixth and seventh races. Bob, who started the meeting with a 
mythical $1,000 bankroll, is at $807.40. 
</P>
<P>
Bob's bet today is a $25 win parlay from Inquisitorial in the third to Great 
Relations in the fifth. 
</P>
<P>
Saturday's Bankroll: $825.40 
</P>
<P>
Saturday's Loss: $18 
</P>
<P>
Curent Bankroll: $807.40 
</P>
</TEXT>
