</P>
<P>
"News 13S reports on Earth Day-related stories. 
</P>
<P>
CABLE 
</P>
<P>
A&amp;E 
</P>
<P>
Ted Danson hosts the new 26-part series, "Challenge of the Seas," which 
examines the role the oceans and its inhabitants play in the balance of the 
Earth's ecology, 5 and 9 p.m. April 22. 
</P>
<P>
DISNEY 
</P>
<P>
Throughout the week, "The Mickey Mouse Club" will focus on environmental 
