children-citizens of North America, South America, Europe, Australia, Africa 
and Asia-travel to Antarctica on "Lilliput Conquers Antarctica," 7:30 p.m. 
April 22. 
</P>
<P>
VH-1 
</P>
<P>
The pop music network has been running daily environmental tips and information 
that will continue through April 22. VH-1 will air musical performances and 
video clips highlighting environmental themes, plus interviews, political 
commentary and looks at environmental issues throughout the weekend, Saturday 
and April 22. 
</P>
