scheduled start in the Long Beach Grand Prix: "I'm fully aware of the 
implications of being the first black in Indy cars, but that's not what it's 
all about. . . the object is to win. Associated Press; Photo, (Bulldog Edition) 
Willy T. Ribbs 
</P>
